name: DOOMSDAYX Gen 01 Haleek Maul Platinum NFT

metadata.name: DOOMSDAYX Gen 01: Haleek Maul Platinum NFT #1
metadata.description:
This Platinum Producer NFT entitles the holder to behind-the-scenes access to the making of the "VERIFIED" music video, governance rights, a downloadable video treatment, AMA’s with the production team, live stream into the Barbados set, early screening and more. 
 Platinum NFT holders also get exponential governance rights and actual producer credit in the video.
